2018 marked the 18th year of the annual event, and simulcasting has changed the way that people are able to ‘attend’ events like this – after all, thousands more guests benefitted from the experience than the mere 150 that the venue was able to physically hold in Atlanta. Just another example of how tech is affecting the events industry. Our Worx Group Managing Director, Jessica MacRoberts, Shares Her Thoughts On Hosting A Simulcast Conference. Read it here: https://www.wrxgrp.co.za/simulcast-conferences/<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1905/496078-625x625.jpg" alt="Simulcast conferences - thoughts from our MD" width="625" height="625">